1. In order to know which versions of Android are in most current use, you can
  visit the webpage developer.android.com/about/dashboards.
Ans: True

2. If you need to support a different layout when the view changes to landscape,
  in which folder should the new layout be placed?
Ans: layout-land

3. You control the display on large-screen devices by creating specially named resource
  directories to contain alternative definition files for layouts and dimensions.
Ans: True

4. When creating a new class that extends from Fragment, which create method will you overload?
Ans: onCreateView()
